    <div class="uk-grid-column-small uk-grid-row-large uk-child-width-1-3@s uk-text-center" uk-grid>
        <div>
            <div id="k">
                <i class="fas fa-eye fa-5x"></i>
                <h2 class="uk-margin-medium-top uk-text-light">Pantau</h2>
                <p>Lelang barang selalu dipantau selama 24 jam, jangan khawatir lelang diabaikan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div id="k">
                <i class="fas fa-phone-volume fa-5x"></i>
                <h2 class="uk-margin-medium-top uk-text-light">Dihubungi Langsung</h2>
